            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Daniel.9:1-11:1",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EDaniel%209%3A1-11%3A1%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_1%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EDaniel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EDaniel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Prayer%20for%20His%20People%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20was%20the%20first%20year%20of%20the%20reign%20of%20Darius%20the%20Mede%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Ahasuerus%2C%20who%20became%20king%20of%20the%20Babylonians.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Chaldeans.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_2%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EDuring%20the%20first%20year%20of%20his%20reign%2C%20I%2C%20Daniel%2C%20learned%20from%20reading%20the%20word%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20as%20revealed%20to%20Jeremiah%20the%20prophet%2C%20that%20Jerusalem%20must%20lie%20desolate%20for%20seventy%20years.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20See%20Jer%2025%3A11-12%3B%2029%3A10.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_3%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20I%20turned%20to%20the%20Lord%20God%20and%20pleaded%20with%20him%20in%20prayer%20and%20fasting.%20I%20also%20wore%20rough%20burlap%20and%20sprinkled%20myself%20with%20ashes.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_4%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20prayed%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20my%20God%20and%20confessed%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3BLord%2C%20you%20are%20a%20great%20and%20awesome%20God!%20You%20always%20fulfill%20your%20covenant%20and%20keep%20your%20promises%20of%20unfailing%20love%20to%20those%20who%20love%20you%20and%20obey%20your%20commands.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_5%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20we%20have%20sinned%20and%20done%20wrong.%20We%20have%20rebelled%20against%20you%20and%20scorned%20your%20commands%20and%20regulations.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_6%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EWe%20have%20refused%20to%20listen%20to%20your%20servants%20the%20prophets%2C%20who%20spoke%20on%20your%20authority%20to%20our%20kings%20and%20princes%20and%20ancestors%20and%20to%20all%20the%20people%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_7%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BLord%2C%20you%20are%20in%20the%20right%3B%20but%20as%20you%20see%2C%20our%20faces%20are%20covered%20with%20shame.%20This%20is%20true%20of%20all%20of%20us%2C%20including%20the%20people%20of%20Judah%20and%20Jerusalem%20and%20all%20Israel%2C%20scattered%20near%20and%20far%2C%20wherever%20you%20have%20driven%20us%20because%20of%20our%20disloyalty%20to%20you.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_8%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EO%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20we%20and%20our%20kings%2C%20princes%2C%20and%20ancestors%20are%20covered%20with%20shame%20because%20we%20have%20sinned%20against%20you.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_9%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20Lord%20our%20God%20is%20merciful%20and%20forgiving%2C%20even%20though%20we%20have%20rebelled%20against%20him.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_10%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EWe%20have%20not%20obeyed%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God%2C%20for%20we%20have%20not%20followed%20the%20instructions%20he%20gave%20us%20through%20his%20servants%20the%20prophets.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_11%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20Israel%20has%20disobeyed%20your%20instruction%20and%20turned%20away%2C%20refusing%20to%20listen%20to%20your%20voice.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BSo%20now%20the%20solemn%20curses%20and%20judgments%20written%20in%20the%20Law%20of%20Moses%2C%20the%20servant%20of%20God%2C%20have%20been%20poured%20down%20on%20us%20because%20of%20our%20sin.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_12%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20have%20kept%20your%20word%20and%20done%20to%20us%20and%20our%20rulers%20exactly%20as%20you%20warned.%20Never%20has%20there%20been%20such%20a%20disaster%20as%20happened%20in%20Jerusalem.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_13%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EEvery%20curse%20written%20against%20us%20in%20the%20Law%20of%20Moses%20has%20come%20true.%20Yet%20we%20have%20refused%20to%20seek%20mercy%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God%20by%20turning%20from%20our%20sins%20and%20recognizing%20his%20truth.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_14%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20brought%20upon%20us%20the%20disaster%20he%20prepared.%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God%20was%20right%20to%20do%20all%20of%20these%20things%2C%20for%20we%20did%20not%20obey%20him.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_15%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3BLord%20our%20God%2C%20you%20brought%20lasting%20honor%20to%20your%20name%20by%20rescuing%20your%20people%20from%20Egypt%20in%20a%20great%20display%20of%20power.%20But%20we%20have%20sinned%20and%20are%20full%20of%20wickedness.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_16%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20view%20of%20all%20your%20faithful%20mercies%2C%20Lord%2C%20please%20turn%20your%20furious%20anger%20away%20from%20your%20city%20Jerusalem%2C%20your%20holy%20mountain.%20All%20the%20neighboring%20nations%20mock%20Jerusalem%20and%20your%20people%20because%20of%20our%20sins%20and%20the%20sins%20of%20our%20ancestors.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_17%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3Bour%20God%2C%20hear%20your%20servant%26%23x2019%3Bs%20prayer!%20Listen%20as%20I%20plead.%20For%20your%20own%20sake%2C%20Lord%2C%20smile%20again%20on%20your%20desolate%20sanctuary.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_18%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3Bmy%20God%2C%20lean%20down%20and%20listen%20to%20me.%20Open%20your%20eyes%20and%20see%20our%20despair.%20See%20how%20your%20city%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20city%20that%20bears%20your%20name%26%23x2014%3Blies%20in%20ruins.%20We%20make%20this%20plea%2C%20not%20because%20we%20deserve%20help%2C%20but%20because%20of%20your%20mercy.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_19%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3BLord%2C%20hear.%20O%26%23xA0%3BLord%2C%20forgive.%20O%26%23xA0%3BLord%2C%20listen%20and%20act!%20For%20your%20own%20sake%2C%20do%20not%20delay%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3Bmy%20God%2C%20for%20your%20people%20and%20your%20city%20bear%20your%20name.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_20%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EGabriel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Message%20about%20the%20Anointed%20One%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20went%20on%20praying%20and%20confessing%20my%20sin%20and%20the%20sin%20of%20my%20people%2C%20pleading%20with%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20my%20God%20for%20Jerusalem%2C%20his%20holy%20mountain.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_21%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20I%20was%20praying%2C%20Gabriel%2C%20whom%20I%20had%20seen%20in%20the%20earlier%20vision%2C%20came%20swiftly%20to%20me%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20evening%20sacrifice.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_22%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20explained%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BDaniel%2C%20I%20have%20come%20here%20to%20give%20you%20insight%20and%20understanding.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_23%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20moment%20you%20began%20praying%2C%20a%20command%20was%20given.%20And%20now%20I%20am%20here%20to%20tell%20you%20what%20it%20was%2C%20for%20you%20are%20very%20precious%20to%20God.%20Listen%20carefully%20so%20that%20you%20can%20understand%20the%20meaning%20of%20your%20vision.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_24%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BA%20period%20of%20seventy%20sets%20of%20seven%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A24a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eseventy%26%23xA0%3Bsevens.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20been%20decreed%20for%20your%20people%20and%20your%20holy%20city%20to%20finish%20their%20rebellion%2C%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20their%20sin%2C%20to%20atone%20for%20their%20guilt%2C%20to%20bring%20in%20everlasting%20righteousness%2C%20to%20confirm%20the%20prophetic%20vision%2C%20and%20to%20anoint%20the%20Most%20Holy%20Place.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A24b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Most%20Holy%20One.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_9_25%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20listen%20and%20understand!%20Seven%20sets%20of%20seven%20plus%20sixty-two%20sets%20of%20seven%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A25a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3ESeven%20sevens%20plus%20sixty-two%26%23xA0%3Bsevens.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsp